<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1519,1654]" pageId="9" pageNumber="556">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,552,1519,1545]" pageId="9" pageNumber="556">Report as epibiont on bryozoans:</emphasis>
This species was reported as epibiont on marine bryozoans 
<taxonomicName baseAuthorityName="Pallas" baseAuthorityYear="1766" class="Gymnolaemata" family="Electridae" genus="Einhornia" kingdom="Animalia" order="Cheilostomatida" pageId="9" pageNumber="556" phylum="Bryozoa" rank="species" species="crustulenta">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="556">Einhornia crustulenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(reported as 
<taxonomicName box="[354,669,1555,1581]" class="Oligohymenophorea" family="Ellobiophryidae" genus="Membraneipora" kingdom="Protozoa" order="Peritrichida" pageId="9" pageNumber="556" phylum="Ciliophora" rank="species" species="crustulenta">
<emphasis box="[354,669,1555,1581]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="556">Membraneipora crustulenta</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
) in Kiel Bay, the North Sea (
<bibRefCitation author="Precht, H." box="[995,1132,1555,1582]" pageId="9" pageNumber="556" pagination="405 - 474" refId="ref7417" refString="Precht, H. (1935) Epizoen der Kieler Bucht. Nova Acta Leopoldina, 3, 405 - 474." type="journal article" year="1935">Precht 1935</bibRefCitation>
)
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="9.[151,1436,1519,1654]" pageId="9" pageNumber="556">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,721,1591,1617]" pageId="9" pageNumber="556">Report as epibiont on other hosts/substrata:</emphasis>
